  ],
  "remarks": "State Unitary Enterprise of the Donetsk People’s Republic “Komtel” (SUE DPR “KOMTEL”) is a telecom operator operating in the illegally occupied region of Ukraine of Donetsk. It was founded by the so-called “Donetsk People’s Republic” and is managed by the Ministry of Communication of the so-called “Donetsk People’s Republic”. It provides telecommunications services, including to authorities of the so-called “Donetsk People’s Republic”, and it facilitated the holding of the so-called referendum on annexation to the Russian Federation.",
  "@context": "https://www.ammitto.org/ontology/context.jsonld"
}